description=Dynamic game-aware performance engine. Auto-detects games and switches profiles (render thread pinning, uclamp boost, GPU rail lock, 4-thread rendering). iOS-style frame consistency, Qualcomm feature unlock (SilkyScrolls, sPLH, AdaptLaunch), Goodix 480Hz HTSR, IRQ affinity, UFS/DRAM/L3 tuning. Xiaomi 14 Civi (chenfeng) SM8635.
